---
const base = '/ThesisArcPro';
---
<section class="commit">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="commit__eyebrow">Our Commitment</p>
    <h2 class="commit__title">Academic Integrity & Ethical Standards</h2>

    <div class="commit__preview">
      <p>Are you navigating the complexities of your dissertation or thesis? We understand the unique pressures of graduate-level research: rigorous academic standards, complex data analysis, and the weight of your academic future. ThesisArcPro provides a specialized research consultancy service designed to support you through every stage of your journey. Unlike standard writing services, we act as your academic partner, helping you structure, refine, and master your research.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="commit__full" id="commitFull" style="display:none;">

      <div class="commit__two-col">
        <div>
          <h3>Our Approach: Research Mentorship, Not Just Writing</h3>
          <p>Because a Master's dissertation or PhD thesis is vastly different from a standard essay, we offer specialized levels of support tailored to the complexity of your project. Our "Consultancy-First" model ensures you receive expert guidance that aligns with your university's integrity policies.</p>

          <h3>Specialized Academic Expertise</h3>
          <p>We position our service as a learning and development tool. We do not tolerate plagiarism; we provide original, guided research support to help you enhance your own writing skills.</p>
          <p>Our integrity-first process includes:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Originality Assurance:</strong> Every consultation is based on original synthesis of your research data.</li>
            <li><strong>Ethical Guidance:</strong> We help you structure and format your work in compliance with your department's specific guidelines.</li>
            <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> We encourage you to use our guidance as a template to improve your academic voice, ensuring your final submission is a true reflection of your efforts.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Master Your Research Journey Today</h3>
          <p>Don't let complex formatting or data analysis hurdles stall your academic progress. ThesisArcPro is here to help you cross the finish line with confidence.</p>
          <p>Need help with your methodology or thesis structure? <a href={`${base}/contact`}>Place your order</a> and let's discuss your project requirements.</p>
          <p>Let's make your academic journey clearer, more structured, and successful.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3>Specialized Academic Expertise</h3>
          <p>ThesisArcPro stands out by focusing on the depth of research rather than the volume of assignments. Our consultants come from diverse, high-level academic backgrounds, allowing us to manage even the most specialized topics with precision and technical accuracy.</p>
          <p>Currently, we provide specialized support in:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Social Sciences:</strong> Psychology, Sociology, and Education.</li>
            <li><strong>Business & Management:</strong> Entrepreneurship, Strategic Management, and Organizational Behavior.</li>
            <li><strong>Professional Fields:</strong> Nursing, Healthcare, and Legal Research.</li>
            <li><strong>Academic Foundations:</strong> Methodology design, APA/Harvard/OSCOLA formatting, and literature synthesis.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Why Graduate Students Choose ThesisArcPro</h3>
          <p>We know that trusting someone with your thesis is a major decision. Our vetting process ensures you are paired with a professional consultant who values your academic success.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Expert Research Consultants:</strong> Every member of our team is highly qualified with proven experience in research design and academic writing.</li>
            <li><strong>Collaborative Process:</strong> You aren't just "placing an order." You are engaging in a strategy session. We work with you to ensure your project meets university standards.</li>
            <li><strong>Deadline-Driven Results:</strong> We understand that your submission date is non-negotiable. Our consultancy is structured to ensure steady progress.</li>
            <li><strong>Privacy & Professionalism:</strong> Your research is your intellectual property. All consultations are strictly confidential.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <button class="commit__toggle" id="commitToggle">Read more ▾</button>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.commit {
  background: var(--bg-body, #ffffff);
  padding: 3.5rem 0;
  border-top: 1px solid #eef2f7;
}
.commit__eyebrow {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  color: var(--color-main-light, #6d7483);
  margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
}
.commit__title {
  font-family: var(--font-heading, 'Poppins', sans-serif);
  font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 3vw, 1.6rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--color-main, #303b4f);
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.commit__preview {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.commit__preview p {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--color-main-light, #6d7483);
  line-height: 1.7;
  text-align: center;
}

/* ── Full content (hidden by default, toggled by button) ── */
.commit__full {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 1.5rem auto 0;
}
.commit__two-col {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 2.5rem;
}
.commit__full h3 {
  font-family: var(--font-heading, 'Poppins', sans-serif);
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--color-main, #303b4f);
  margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem;
}
.commit__full h3:first-child {
  margin-top: 0;
}
.commit__full p {
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  color: var(--color-main, #303b4f);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
}
.commit__full ul {
  margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 1.2rem;
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  color: var(--color-main, #303b4f);
  line-height: 1.7;
}
.commit__full li {
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
.commit__full a {
  color: var(--color-secondary, #046fcd);
  font-weight: 600;
}

/* ── Toggle button ── */
.commit__toggle {
  display: block;
  margin: 1.5rem auto 0;
  background: none;
  border: none;
  color: var(--color-secondary, #046fcd);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  cursor: pointer;
  padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
  transition: color 0.2s;
}
.commit__toggle:hover {
  color: #0361b3;
}

@media (max-width: 700px) {
  .commit__two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
}
</style>

<script>
  const toggle = document.getElementById('commitToggle');
  const full = document.getElementById('commitFull');
  let open = false;

  toggle?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    open = !open;
    if (full) full.style.display = open ? 'block' : 'none';
    if (toggle) toggle.textContent = open ? 'Show less ▴' : 'Read more ▾';
  });
</script>